#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:2
msgid "Auxiliary Interfaces"
msgstr "辅助接口"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:5
msgid "Registering an Interface"
msgstr "注册接口"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:7
msgid ""
"Class interfaces can be registered if you want to guarantee that script "
"classes implement a specific set of class methods. Interfaces can be easier "
"to use when working with script classes from the application, but they are "
"not necessary as the application can easily enumerate available methods and "
"properties even without the interfaces."
msgstr ""
"如果您希望确保脚本类实现一组特定的类方法，可以注册类接口。在应用程序中处理脚"
"本类时，接口可能更易于使用，但它们并非必需，因为即使没有接口，应用程序也可以"
"轻松枚举可用的方法和属性。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:20
msgid ""
"Unlike the raw AngelScript interface, you don't need to add the class name "
"into the declaration of member ``funcdef`` for asbind20."
msgstr ""
"与原始 AngelScript 接口不同，asbind20的接口不需要将类名添加到成员 "
"``funcdef`` 的声明中。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:24
msgid "Type Aliases"
msgstr "类型别名"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:26
msgid ""
"Function definitions can be registered when you wish to allow the script to "
"pass function pointers to the application, e.g. to implement callback "
"routines."
msgstr ""
"当您希望允许脚本将函数指针传递给应用程序时，可以注册函数定义，例如实现回调例"
"程。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:29
msgid ""
"Enumeration types and ``typedef``\\ s can also be registered to improve "
"readability of the scripts."
msgstr "枚举类型和 ``typedef``\\ s 也可以注册以提高脚本的可读性。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:0
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:36
msgid "Example code:"
msgstr "示例代码："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:49
msgid "Enumerations"
msgstr "枚举"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:66
msgid ""
"Up until version 2.39, AngelScript used a 32-bit integer to store the "
"underlying value of enums, before it supported customizable underlying "
"types. Please make sure those values don't overflow or underflow."
msgstr ""
"在 2.39 版本之前，AngelScript 在支持可自定义底层类型之前，使用 32 位整数来存"
"储枚举的底层值。请确保这些值不会溢出或下溢。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:70
msgid ""
"Besides, the library provides a convenient interface for generating string "
"representation of enum value at compile-time."
msgstr "此外，该库提供了一个便捷的接口，用于在编译时生成枚举值的字符串表示。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:72
msgid "The following code is equivalent to the above one:"
msgstr "以下代码与上述代码等效："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:81
msgid ""
"However, as static reflection is still waiting for C++26, this feature "
"relies on compiler extension. It's guaranteed to work on mainstream "
"compilers (MSVC, GCC, and Clang). **It has some limitations**. For example, "
"it cannot generate string representation for enums with same value."
msgstr ""
"然而，由于静态反射仍在等待 C++26，此特性依赖于编译器扩展。它保证能在主流编译"
"器（MSVC、GCC 和 Clang）上正常工作。**它有一些限制**。例如，它无法为具有相同"
"值的枚举生成字符串表示。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:93
msgid ""
"Since the version 2.39, AngelScript supports enumerations with custom "
"underlying types."
msgstr "自 2.39 版本起，AngelScript 支持具有自定义底层类型的枚举。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:95
msgid ""
"You can register them by ``enum_underlying``, which is an alias of "
"``enum_<Enum, std::underlying_type_t<Enum>>``."
msgstr ""
"您可以通过 ``enum_underlying`` 来注册它们，它是 ``enum_<Enum, "
"std::underlying_type_t<Enum>>`` 的别名。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:114
msgid ""
"If you need to interact these enums from C++ side, the enums with custom "
"underlying type :ref:`need to specify the conversion rules <custom-rule-for-"
"enum-underlying>`."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要从 C++ 端与这些枚举进行交互，具有自定义底层类型的枚举 :ref:`需要指"
"定转换规则 <custom-rule-for-enum-underlying>`。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:118
msgid "Listener API"
msgstr "Listener API"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:121
msgid ""
"The listener API described in this section is **experimental**. Its "
"interface may change in future releases."
msgstr ""
"本节描述的 Listener API 是**实验性的**。其接口在未来版本中可能会发生变化。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:123
msgid ""
"Every binding generator (``value_class``, ``ref_class``, ``global``, "
"``enum_``, ``interface``) accepts an optional ``Listener`` template "
"parameter. When an entity is registered, the generator invokes the "
"corresponding callback on the listener, passing itself and the returned "
"value from AngelScript API."
msgstr ""
"每个绑定生成器（``value_class``、``ref_class``、``global``、``enum_``、"
"``interface``）都接受一个可选的 ``Listener`` 模板参数。当实体被注册时，生成器"
"会在监听器上调用相应的回调，传递自身以及 AngelScript API 返回的值。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:127
msgid "This allows you to:"
msgstr "这使您可以："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:129
msgid "Record what was registered for logging or debugging"
msgstr "记录已注册的内容以供日志记录或调试"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:130
msgid "Validate registered entities"
msgstr "验证已注册的实体"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:131
msgid "Collect metadata about the bound interface"
msgstr "收集有关绑定接口的元数据"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:134
msgid "Defining a listener"
msgstr "定义监听器"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:136
msgid ""
"A listener is a class that implements any subset of the following callback "
"methods. Each is optional — if omitted, the call is silently skipped (no-op)."
msgstr ""
"监听器是一个实现了以下任意回调方法子集的类。每个方法都是可选的——如果省略，"
"调用将被静默跳过（无操作）。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:159
msgid ""
"The ``gen`` parameter is a reference to the binding generator instance (e.g. "
"``global``, ``value_class<T>``). Use it to query the engine, type info, or "
"the generator's type ID."
msgstr ""
"``gen`` 参数是对绑定生成器实例（例如 ``global``、``value_class<T>``）的引用。"
"使用它可以查询引擎、类型信息或生成器的类型 ID。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:162
msgid ""
"The ``int`` parameter is the AngelScript ID returned by the registration "
"call:"
msgstr "``int`` 参数是注册调用返回的 AngelScript ID："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:164
msgid "Non-negative values indicate success."
msgstr "非负值表示成功。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:165
msgid ""
"By default, negative values will throw a ``std::system_error``. Define "
"``ASBIND20_CONFIG_NO_THROW_ON_BAD_BINDING`` to suppress this."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，负值会抛出 ``std::system_error``。定义 "
"``ASBIND20_CONFIG_NO_THROW_ON_BAD_BINDING`` 可以抑制此行为。"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:169
msgid "Using a listener"
msgstr "使用监听器"

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:171
msgid ""
"Pass the listener as a template parameter and retrieve it with "
"``get_listener()``:"
msgstr ""
"将监听器作为模板参数传递，并使用 ``get_listener()`` 获取它："

#: ../../doc/aux_interface.rst:184
msgid ""
"Listeners are default-constructed unless you pass an instance to the "
"generator's constructor:"
msgstr ""
"监听器是默认构造的，除非您将实例传递给生成器的构造函数："

